{"tid":1428136,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當支爆臨近，本土是你們唯一的出路","createTime":"2019-08-07T08:56:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T05:46:54.000Z","uid":245274,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"83e3ff2ffc6b8561924659ea7a7e9011d10a7deb","tid":1428136,"uid":245274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:56:17.000Z","msg":"中美貿易戰繼續升溫， 而中國的劣勢繼續加劇。<br />\n內地各地政府已經還不起債務，人民幣即將貶值。<br />\n香港只需等到10月美國國會修正關係法，港元就會被脱勾，而各位的財產會被收歸國有。<br />\n香港的中產，低層，警察，都會成為中共的棄子。<br />\n當中只有最接近共產黨的一群人，能在枯竭後的香港繼續欺壓本土人。<br />\n而大部份人會被共產黨背叛，成為行屍走肉，失去尊嚴，希望，思想。<br />\n<br />\n為了不進入滅亡的未來，我建議<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所有香港人</span>對抗共產黨，讓美國知道香港與中共的不同。以在日後支爆時，香港能作為70年代的位置，保持現有的生活水平。<br />\n<br />\n無論是<br />\n警察，平民， 黑社會， 鄉紳，資本家<br />\n或是家人，朋友，同學，<br />\n上司，同事，下屬。<br />\n<br />\n你們都應當為自己的未來<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">開拓出路</span><br />\n<br />\n祝各位有幸福美滿的人生"},{"pid":"986c0b89edbd7e08b8dbfd811d1689f1cf3cda64","tid":1428136,"uid":268019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:03:34.000Z","msg":"你 up 乜鳩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d36ccfbd95465899e24417a239e7c61df33dac","tid":1428136,"uid":245274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:34:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438754</a>"},{"pid":"084818cb69b64383f71097e50aa0753d0fe5404a","tid":1428136,"uid":245274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:35:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439007</a>"},{"pid":"0e2b99a1b2268579d8fca42627ce6466b1c15781","tid":1428136,"uid":267004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:52:15.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"6a8c5088265b15e01fb1f012047662efbdefb7ac","tid":1428136,"uid":245274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:53:40.0